info.description: # Pykami A python module that parses kami into HTML. ## Usage Simply run `pykami.parse()`, which takes a string containing a KAMI input and outputs a string containing the corresponding HTML output. ```python import pykami print(pykami.parse("*bold text*")) // bold text ``` For the kami specification, read the [kami-parser readme](https://github.com/lilith-in-starlight/kami-parser/).
